London Law Firms Clyde & Co., Barlow Lyde May Merge, Times Says

-- B y   M a r i a   K o l e s n i k o v a
-- 
2011-06-04T12:32:30Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-04/london-law-firms-clyde-co-barlow-lyde-may-merge-times-says.html
London-based law firms Clyde & Co LLP
and Barlow Lyde & Gilbert LLP may agree to merge as early as
this month, creating a company with more than 300 million pounds
($493 million) in annual revenue, the London-based Times
 reported , citing chief executive officers of the two companies.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Maria Kolesnikova in London at 
 mkolesnikova@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Claudia Carpenter at 
 ccarpenter@bloomberg.net . 